Lions Promo & Activation celebrates creativity that brings brands to life. Entries needed to demonstrate ideas that generate interaction; where consumer participation in an activity serves to promote a product or service. #CannesLions2017: Promo & Activation Lions shortlistThe Cannes Lions Promo & Activation shortlist has been released...17 hours ago The Grand Prix went to the Boost Mobile&#x2019;s &#x2018;Boost your voice&#x2019;, by 180LA Santa Monica. Boost Mobile's Promo & Activation Lions Grand Prix-winning work.click to enlarge The campaign promoted Boost stores as polling stations in under-served areas populated by low-income and minority voters in a move towards equal voting access. View the full table of winning work below: Promo & Activation Lions winners EntrantTitleClientProductAward180LA, Santa MonicaBOOST YOUR VOICEBOOST MOBILEPROMOTE BOOST STORES AS POLLING STATIONSGrand Prix SAATCHI & SAATCHI, New YorkBRADSHAW STAINP&GTIDEGold LionGREY NEW YORK / PROCTER & GAMBLE, BostonHANDLE WITH CAREPROCTER & GAMBLEGILLETTEGold LionBETC, ParisLIKE MY ADDICTIONADDICT'AIDEADDICT'AIDEGold LionMcCANN NEW YORKFEARLESS GIRLSTATE STREET GLOBAL ADVISORSSHE ETFGold LionSAATCHI & SAATCHI, New YorkBRADSHAW STAINP&GTIDEGold LionFRED & FARID PARISLIB DES R FUGI SLIB RATIONNEWSPAPERSGold LionGREY COLOMBIA, Bogot PAYPHONE BANKTIGO-UNEPAYPHONE MICRO SAVINGS ACCOUNTGold Lionadam&eveDDB, LondonGIVE THE RAINBOWMARSSKITTLESGold LionSAATCHI & SAATCHI, New YorkBRADSHAW STAINP&GTIDEGold LionCLEMENGER BBDO MELBOURNEMEET GRAHAMTRANSPORT ACCIDENT COMMISSION VICTORIATRANSPORT ACCIDENT COMMISSION VICTORIAGold LionMcCANN NEW YORKFEARLESS GIRLSTATE STREET GLOBAL ADVISORSSHE ETFGold LionBETC, ParisLIKE MY ADDICTIONADDICT'AIDEADDICT'AIDEGold LionGOODBY SILVERSTEIN & PARTNERS, San FranciscoCHEETOS MUSEUMCHEETOSCHEETOSGold LionGREY NEW YORK / PROCTER & GAMBLE, BostonHANDLE WITH CAREPROCTER & GAMBLEGILLETTEGold LionOGILVY NEW YORKTHE REFUGEE NATIONAMNESTY INTERNATIONALAWARNESS AROUND THE REFUGEE CA